) Present in most of Europe and widespread in large areas, absent on the Atlantic coast of southern Spain and Portugal , in the British Isles and the Baltic areas. Outside Europe, it is present in Asia Minor , East and West Turkestan, Siberia (Yakutia, Transbaikalia) and in the Chinese Altai at the Far East of Russia ( Witt & Ronkay 2011 ).
